dcterms:description: MIDFIELD is a longitudinal student unit-record dataset from 1988-2018 for all undergraduate, degree-seeking students at partner institutions. It includes demographic data, information about major concentration, enrollment, graduation, and students' performance.
dcterms:title: MIDFIELD (Multiple-Institution Database for Investigating Engineering Longitudinal Development)
